# Web Dashboard

React SPA for history-repository JSON. Uses HashRouter (static deploy, no SSR).

## Design system

Follow `design-system/actions-insights/MASTER.md` for colors, typography, and spacing. Check `design-system/pages/[page-name].md` for page-specific overrides.

## Structure

- Routes in `web/src/App.tsx`
- Pages in `web/src/pages/`, components in `web/src/components/`
- Data types from `@actions-insights/history-models`

## Commands

```bash
npm test --workspace=@actions-insights/web
npm run build --workspace=@actions-insights/web
```

## Gotcha

`web/src/version.ts` is generated by `scripts/write-version.mjs` (gitignored). Do not create or commit it manually.
